*mpg123-0.59s-r4 (14 Sep 2004)

  14 Sep 2004; <solar@gentoo.org> +files/mpg123-0.59s-CAN-2004-0805.patch,
  +mpg123-0.59s-r4.ebuild:
  security bump. bug #63079 : A malicious formatted mp3/2 causes mpg123 to fail
  header checks, this may allow arbitrary code to be executed with the privilege
  of the user trying to play the mp3.

